sequenceDiagram
    participant HE as handleExecution
    participant EG as errgroup
    participant Producer
    participant Pipe as eventpipe<br/>(buffered chan)
    participant Consumer
    participant BQ as Broadcast Queue

    HE->>EG: errgroup.WithContext(ctx)

    par
        EG->>Producer: go producer(egCtx)
        Producer->>Producer: agent.Execute yields event
        Producer->>Pipe: pipe.Write(event)
    and
        EG->>Consumer: go consumer(egCtx)
        Pipe-->>Consumer: pipe.Read() → event
        Consumer->>Consumer: processor.Process(event)
        Consumer->>BQ: broadcast.Write(processed event)
    end

    Note over Producer,Pipe: producer keeps yielding events

    Producer->>Producer: agent yields terminal event
    Producer->>Pipe: pipe.Write(terminal event)
    Pipe-->>Consumer: pipe.Read() → terminal event
    Consumer->>Consumer: processor.Process → ExecutionResult set
    Consumer-->>EG: return errConsumerStopped

    Note over EG: errgroup cancels egCtx

    Producer->>Pipe: pipe.Write(next event)
    Note over Producer,Pipe: write succeeds if buffer has space!<br/>producer must check ctx on next iteration
    Producer->>Producer: agent.Execute checks ctx.Done()
    Producer-->>EG: return ctx.Err()

    EG-->>HE: group.Wait() returns
    Note over HE: processorResult set → return (result, nil)<br/>errConsumerStopped is filtered out

    HE->>HE: executor.Cleanup(ctx, result, err)
    HE->>HE: execution.result.setValue(result)
    HE->>HE: cleanupExecution (destroy queue, signalDone)